~ start
do MusicController.vol_reset()
do MusicController.play_zulie_theme()
do get_tree().call_group("Zulie", "crouch_l")
do get_tree().call_group("VagabondActor", "crouch_noweapon_l")
Vagabond: [shake rate=20 level=10]Nghh...[/shake] How embarrasing...I should be giving that coward what he deserves, not cowering and getting stitches!
set TalkScenes.zulie_talk.dialogue_resource = load("res://dialogue/zulie_precredits.dialogue")
set TalkScenes.zulie_talk.start()
=> END